org.franca.core.franca

Interface FMapType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, FModelElement, FType, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FMapTypeImpl

    public interface FMapType
extends FType
    A representation of the model object 'FMap Type'. The Franca map type (sometimes "map" is also called "dictionary"). This is a collection type which maps objects of a e[key] type to objects of a e[value] type in constant time.

    The following features are supported:

    • Key Type
    • Value Type

    See Also:
